 How to Add Credentials to the Windows Credential Manager Vault?

Adding Git credentials on Windows Ideally, you should enter: git config --global credential.helper manager-core Then your password would be stored in the Windows Credential Manager
upport for password authentication was removed on August 13, 2021. Please use a personal access token instead. This kind of error is shown when you push in github using password authentication now. So to fix this we can use access token on windows.

